<example>
  <title>Dosage Calculator</title>
  <program>
age = int(input("Enter your age: "))

if age <= 12 : 
    dosage = 1  # execute this if True
else
    dosage = 3  # execute this if False

print("The dosage is", dosage, "tablet(s)")

  </program>
  <description>Find the dosage based on input age using one-way selection.  An one-way selection has a default condition (normal dosage) and a special condition (child dosage)</description>
